# Dashboard App

## Purpose

The `dashboard` app is a Next.js application for managing stores, products, orders, and customers. It's the main admin interface for the Dukkani platform.

## Structure

```text
apps/dashboard/src/
├── app/
│   ├── [lang]/
│   │   ├── (auth)/            # Login + onboarding flows
│   │   ├── (dashboard)/       # Protected merchant routes
│   │   └── layout.tsx
│   └── manifest.ts
├── components/
│   ├── auth/
│   ├── app/                   # Feature UI (products, orders, onboarding, settings, …)
│   ├── layout/
│   └── shared/
├── shared/
│   ├── api/                   # orpc client, auth-client, mutations, queries, error-handler
│   │   ├── orpc.ts            # `api` and `queryClient` exports
│   │   ├── orpc.server.ts     # Server-side oRPC utilities
│   │   ├── session.server.ts  # Server-side session helpers
│   │   ├── auth-client.ts     # Better Auth client
│   │   ├── error-handler.ts   # Centralized `handleAPIError`
│   │   ├── mutations.ts       # `appMutations` object (all domain mutations with invalidation)
│   │   └── queries.ts         # `appQueries` object (all domain query options)
